Total Build Cost approximately  £1100
This is a component list for the can seamer, assuming you have a compressor.  Total cost was £680, the most expensive item was the air cylinders. The steel cost £336 and a cutting list can be found on the Sketch Up file. I used some steel tube from a cellar cooler for the fill tubes and I had a box full of JG 3/8 fittings and pipe so you will need to figure out what you need to plumb yours up. 

